    public class SpringMyBatisCacheStoreWithChildEntitiesWriteOnceOnly
extends SpringMyBatisCacheStoreWithChildEntities
    CacheStore implementation class designed to be able to handle relational objects integrated with Spring and MyBatis framework.
    This CacheStore is able to only write once (insert only) to database through Coherence cache, not update, load or delete.
    This CacheStore has higher performance in insert only architecture than SpringMyBatisCacheStoreWithChildEntities.
    Author:
    Shota Yamazaki
